(36, 28, 65, 618, NULL, '<p>Bluestone Apps is a premier mobile application development company delivering the highest performance with unique execution and design process in every app solution it provides.</p><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\">Our History</strong></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Bluestone Apps is the sister company to Knoxweb, which was established in 1996. With the rise of mobile apps in the world of technology, Bluestone Apps became its own entity in 2011. Since that time, our team has been dedicated to providing native and hybrid mobile app solutions to a global clientele. We have obtained expertise in a variety of app categories, including&nbsp;ride share platforms, fitness, audio &amp; video streaming, restaurant ordering, travel, radio stations, user subscriptions, e-commerce, auctions &amp; bidding, food &amp; package delivery, file sharing, health &amp; medical platforms, video chat, social media networks, and more!</span></p><p><br></p><h2><strong style=\"color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\">Our Headquarters</strong></h2><p>Bluestone Apps is located in Knoxville, TN, which is home to the University of Tennessee and neighbor to the Great Smoky Mountains. We also have satellite offices in Minneapolis, MN and San Diego, CA. While some of our clients prefer a local digital agency to create their projects, the vast majority of our valued clientele works with us remotely. Through video conferencing, screen sharing, phone conversations, and emails combined with a trusted project management platform, our team can bring your project to life no matter where you are in the world.</p><p><br></p><h2 class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(28, 28, 28);\">Our Team</strong></h2><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Comprised of over 38 employees, the Bluestone Apps team includes individuals who work in our sales, design, development, testing, and support departments. Our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://web.facebook.com/lo